30b is a road that connects with Mace Blvd from the northwest.  From its intersection with Mace, it makes a few turns northeastwards through the outskirts outskirts of town and becomes County Road 30.  County Road 30 then continues on eastward for a while until it ends (verify please) near Willow Slough Bypass. County Road 30b is part of Yolo Countys County Roads County Road System.

